{"about_the_game":"Pardon or kill. Let the madness begin!<br>At the edge of despair, lurks the unsettling past, and an unspeakable truth.<br>What lies hidden in the twisted attractions of the secluded amusement park, Yurukill Land?<br>Who will emerge victorious from its cruel, fiendish games?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733840/extras/ADV\u30cf\u309a\u30fc\u30c8_1.gif?t=1724080922\" /><br><br><strong>Clear Your Name: </strong>Take on the nerfarious attractions of Yurukill Land for a chance to prove your innocence. Partner up with your Executioner and set your sights on emerging victorius from the Yurukill Games. For the victors, absolution awaits.<br><br><strong>Risk Your Life:</strong> Solve puzzles and uncover hints about the crimes you stand accused of, and put it all on the line in Maji-Kill Time\u2014tense life or death cross-examinations. One wrong answer, and all is lost. As you progress, the grim truths of each incident will come to light.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733840/extras/STG\u30cf\u309a\u30fc\u30c8__1_.gif?t=1724080922\" /><br><br><strong>Take to the (Virtual) Skies:</strong> Pilot your Yurukill Fighter through a series of virtual reality challenges. Put your understanding of each case to the test in High-Speed Quizzes: choose the correct lane, and you'll be rewarded with extra lives. In the Prejudice Synapse, present evidence from your investigations, and destroy your Executioner's prejudices. Each top-down shoot \u2018em up section (courtesy of veteran developer G.rev!) ends with a nail-biting Prisoner vs Executioner showdown. Whether you're a shoot 'em up expert or newcomer to the genre, find the perfect challenge to suit your level with a choice of Easy, Normal, and Hell difficulties.<br><br><strong>Run the Gauntlet: </strong>Choose your craft, set the difficulty, buckle up, and blast through shoot 'em up sections from the main game in Score Attack mode. Features global online rankings.<br><br>Original Story / Scenario: Homura Kawamoto / Hikaru Muno<br>Director / Producer: Shinsuke Umeda<br>Character Design: Hiro Kiyohara<br>Soundtrack: Yuko Komiyama<br>Shoot \u2018em up development: G.rev<br><br>*For players wishing to use a Nintendo Switch Pro Controller:<br>Access the Steam Controller Settings menu and enable &quot;Switch Pro Configuration Support,&quot; then disable &quot;Use Nintendo Button Layout.&quot; If a Nintendo Switch Pro Controller is connected via cable while &quot;Disable Steam Input&quot; is active in the game's controller settings, the controller will not function properly. <br>*Internet connection required for online ranking.<br>\u30fbNintendo Switch is a trademark of Nintendo.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Yurukill Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1733840/87b92918ce1ded544328c4345936a2174cbf4529.jpg"},{"name":"Bin-credible Super Collector!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1733840/69421151ab1befa470b8aa63faef6878c4e0d6e8.jpg"},{"name":"SS-Rank Yurukill Fighter -HELL-","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1733840/efca32b1bdfdf67e7c9b05c404d994423ae6fddd.jpg"},{"name":"SS-Rank Yurukill Fighter -NORMAL-","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1733840/3e345765ff8a05a588b68ced97849333710d9b58.jpg"},{"name":"SS-Rank Yurukill Fighter -EASY-","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1733840/a7a1465733716f0921f74e04a61b6d7e6fccc8ae.jpg"},{"name":"Puzzle Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1733840/7617d2166516566707702e546159644ef05396d6.jpg"},{"name":"S-Rank Yurukill Fighter -HELL-","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1733840/a6f7c8799e8f32ad5e